2	//!
3	//! The color-machine blocks feed an arbitrary event sequence through a machine
4	//! and assert the component's core invariants always hold: stored values stay
5	//! in range, states stay within the declared set, and `connect()` never panics.
6	//! The stateless `QrCode` block instead pins its prop->attr mapping across the
7	//! whole input space. Run in the nightly `extended-proptest` job; `#[ignore]`d
8	//! in the fast tier.
